        },
        "text_Mqytwd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/ecopure\" title=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/ecopure\"><strong>EcoPure</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/ecopure\" title=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/ecopure\"><strong>Soil Guard</strong></a> are highly effective petroleum and hydrocarbon cleanup solutions that leverage advanced bioscience and bioremediation methods. These products utilize naturally occurring, non-pathogenic bacteria to break down and remove petroleum compounds and hydrocarbons from contaminated environments.</p><p>When applied to affected areas, the microbial action rapidly accelerates the breakdown process, targeting oil and fuel residues for complete degradation. The specially formulated blend boosts microbial efficiency, resulting in the conversion of contaminants into harmless by-products—leaving behind only carbon dioxide and water.</p><p>This environmentally friendly approach leaves no toxic residue and provides a safe, reliable, and affordable option for cleaning up fuel spills on surfaces such as pavement, concrete, soil, grass, and water. EcoPure and Soil Guard are simple to apply and deliver powerful results without harming the environment.</p><p><strong>Effective Against:</strong></p><ul><li>Gasoline</li><li>Motor oil</li><li>Diesel fuel</li><li>Coal tar</li><li>Crude oil</li><li>Fuel oils</li></ul><p><strong>Applications:</strong></p><ul><li>Petroleum-contaminated wastewater</li><li>Wastewater pumps</li><li>Holding tanks</li><li>Contaminated soil</li><li>Oil and grease separators</li></ul><p><strong>Available Options:</strong></p><ul><li>EcoPure 32 oz</li><li>EcoPure 1 gallon</li><li>Soil Guard 1 gallon</li><li>Soil Guard Powder (for 5 gallons)</li></ul>",
            "text_style": "body"
